FEG copied of Walther PP, and in my opinion the FEG is a better gun and very accurate.  Hammer springs can be bought from Wolfe Springs with the 11 lb just right.  Also higher power recoil springs can reduce kick but with the 32 ACP not necessary.FEGs are very accurate shooters and even better once springs changed out.  I have not changed the springs on this gun.I will ship to another state or location FFL only.  Buyer pays approximately $35 plus insurance for shipping and must send or email copy of Drivers License & FFL.  USPS Money Orders only accpeted.Please email for more info include your name and number if you don't mind.  I will respond to all inquiries so feel free to ask questions.  However, I will be firm on price with this due to rarity ( few out there and most are Import Marked).
